highlights.text: “everything i wanted” by Billie Eilish is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 100 spots at #2.
J Balvin has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “RITMO (Bad Boys For Life)” is the highest at #9.
“Watermelon Sugar” by Harry Styles is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #21.
“Shape of You” by Ed Sheeran has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 150 weeks straight.
